% Phase 2 Strategy Paper Manifest — BibTeX
%
% Machine-readable counterpart of docs/papers/phase-2.md. One @article
% (or @inproceedings / @techreport) entry per Phase 2 strategy paper —
% both the foundational and primary citations where the two differ —
% deduplicated by citation key.
%
% Maintenance: each Phase 2 strategy commit appends the entries needed
% by its paper.md. Session 2H's audit reconciles citation keys here
% against citations in the corresponding paper.md files and against
% the row count in phase-2.md.
%
% Citation key convention: <firstauthorlowercase><year> — e.g.
% moskowitz2012 for Moskowitz/Ooi/Pedersen 2012. Disambiguate by
% appending a letter suffix (moskowitz2012a, moskowitz2012b) only if
% the same first author has multiple cited works in the same year.
%
% Phase 1 citations are NOT mirrored here — they live in each Phase 1
% strategy's paper.md and are out of scope for the Phase 2 manifest.
